Interface CaveWorker

All Known Implementing Classes:
Adventurer, Character, Filler, Miner
public interface CaveWorker

Interface to describe what modifications are allowed by certain characters and actually carry out those modifications, if applicable to a given spot for a given character type. Remember that you don't implement any methods in an interface, you just give the method prototypes.
